WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Why would a character as flamboyant as Ziggy wear such discrete bracelets? 

00:05.500 --> 00:09.500
It turns out that they weren’t Ziggy’s at all. They were David’s. 

00:10.000 --> 00:13.000
For several years, pre and post-Ziggy, 

00:13.500 --> 00:18.000
David wore a pair of Peruvian-made wedding bands on his left wrist. 

00:19.000 --> 00:22.500
Despite losing them several times while performing on stage, 

00:23.000 --> 00:30.000
they were repeatedly returned to him by well-meaning fans once their significance was discovered.